This is officially known as the GOHMIC-ASYLUM and can be installed in any ARC1X scenario/chapter
IT is DESIGNED to PREVENT/WITHSTAND a NIGHTMARE-SCENARIO/REALITY-BREAK in a CRISIS/DDAY.
